## Early game

**Ophelia** on Uranus (Survival) is a natural first stop, since Uranus has the
highest Polymer Bundle drop chance of any planet — nearly every resource pickup
on this Survival is a bundle, and it nets Tellurium on the side for later
weapon builds.

## Mid & late game

**Assur** on the same planet (Dark Sector Survival, Infested Grineer Galleon,
Steel Path) edges Ophelia out for a geared squad: its cramped chokepoints
concentrate the large Infested population that spawns there, and running with
a Nekros or Hydroid to re-roll enemy drops squeezes extra bundles out of every
kill on top of the Dark Sector's resource bonus.

